HEADWORD: footlocker
<hw>foot"lock*er</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a trunk for storing personal
possessions; usually kept at the foot of a bed (as in a military
barracks).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> locker.</syn>⟦br⟧
